docs.lead_paragraph: BOARD OF ALDERMEN. THE EXTENSION OF WORTH-STREET-A NEW MARKET-SITE FOR A COUNTY JAIL-ISSUE OF CENTRAI, PARK STOCK. The Board of Aldermen, last evening, received and referred a remonstrance, signed by propertyowners on Worth-street, against the extension of Worth-street, from Baxter-street to Chatbam-square, until they should have another opportunity to appear and oppose it before the Committee on Streets.

docs.lead_paragraph: The People vs. Felix Sanchez.--A session of the General Term of the Supreme Court was held on Saturday--Justices ROOSEVELT, CLERKE and SUTHERLAND being present. At the opening of the Court, Justice ROOSEVELT delivered the opinion of the Court denying the motion for a new trial lately made in the case of Felix Sanchez.
